<P>THE old gentleman desiring to be left to him|self a few moments, the attorney and the children withdrew&mdash;He offered up some pious ejaculations requesting the blessings so abundantly shower <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> himself might be continued to his children, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> heart overflowed with gratitude for the many <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">|cies he had enjoyed; he petitioned health and pros|perity
