<FRONT>
<DIV1 TYPE="title page">
<PB REF="026108_0129_0FCFAF4F41410B80">
<P>THE INQUISITOR; OR, INVISIBLE RAMBLER.</P>
<P>IN THREE VOLUMES.</P>
<P><HI>By Mrs. ROWSON, author of Victoria.</HI></P>
<P>THE FIRST AMERICAN EDITION.</P>
<P>VOLUME III.</P>
<P>PHILADELPHIA&mdash;PRINTED AND SOLD BY WILLIAM GIBBONS, N^o. 144, NORTH THIRD-STREET.</P>
