<P>O, Hester, you do not know the dreadful cir|cumstances of your brother's death&mdash;alas! my child, he rushed unbidden into the presence of his Maker with multitudes of unrepented crime<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter"> upon his head.</P>
<P>Did he destroy himself? cried <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 span"> of woe changing into that of inexpressible horror.&mdash;Oh! what could tempt him to the dreadful <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">?</P>
