<P>Hester, said he, with a look of horrid firmness, I will unfold to you a tale which it is proper you should know; I may not long continue with you.&mdash;I have been guilty of deeds which will make your tender heart shudder to acknowledge me as a <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">&mdash;On! cursed avarice, it was that which <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 span"> to stain my soul with murder, and to ruin <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 span"> my darling son.&mdash;For him and for thee
