<P>Was Horace murdered! Oh! inhuman wretch, cried Hester&mdash;then where is my sweet Julietta? have you murdered her too?</P>
<P>I hope she still lives, said Vellum; and may your gentle friendship recall her wandering reason, for my cruelty has bereaved her of her senses; and if she is alive, she is a poor, distressed lunatic.</P>
